&lt;p&gt;You combine strategic brand leadership with hands-on execution. You know how to build iconic consumer brands, develop impactful communication platforms, and lead cross-functional teams to deliver outstanding business results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;178&quot; data-end=&quot;276&quot;&gt;This is a hybrid role that requires regular (bi-weekly) on-site collaboration at our Hamburg headquarters.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
