&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You create a strong, authentic visual presence for ESN &amp;amp; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;More Nutrition&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;across social media and digital platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You collaborate closely with the Media Production Team to develop new, engaging social media formats and support content planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You work hand in hand with our athletes and creators to produce relatable, community-driven content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You independently develop creative concepts that fit ESN &amp;amp; More Nutrition’s tone, values, and audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You plan video shoots in detail together with our Creative Leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You independently execute video shoots for YouTube, product integrations, and social media assets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You have professional experience in video production and enjoy working in dynamic, fast-paced environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You have a solid understanding of camera systems, sound recording, and lighting&lt;/li&gt;
