&lt;li&gt;You are confident in analyzing performance data and translating insights into actionable improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You combine a structured, detail-oriented working style with a strong hands-on mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a strong communicator and able to align cross-functional teams effectively&lt;/li&gt;
